    "description": "\u003cdiv class=\"structured-content-rich-text structured-content__module l-align-left l-mar-vert-6 l-sm-mar-vert-4 text-body-medium\"\u003e\n\t\u003cp\u003ePrepare yourself for a new career path as a personal chef. Whether part-time supplemental income, or as a full-time career path, being a personal chef is a rewarding career option with many different avenues to keep your creativity at its peak.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn this  on-line course, you'll learn how to:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eSet Up a Website and Create Your Brand\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eUnderstand regulations and operate legally\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eFind Your First Client\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eNavigate the New Client Meeting\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003ePrepare for your first cooking day\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eAsk for and receive valuable feedback\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eStreamline the Invoicing and Billing Process\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eWe'll also cover a bonus content sections:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e Avoiding Common Personal Chef Pitfalls\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eProviding Personal Chef Service during Covid-19 \u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eEach section will allow time for Q\u0026amp;A so specific questions you have may be answered.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou will also have access to downloadable content including a Client Preferences Worksheet, Kitchen Inventory Sheet, and a Sample Client contract. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you can't attend the entire live summit, you will receive access to watch the recording at a later time.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e",
